Description: GTK+2 client for the Music Player Daemon (MPD)
DescDetail: <<
 Ario is a full featured client for MPD (Music Player Daemon). The interface used
 to browse the library is inspired by Rhythmbox but Ario aims to be much
 lighter and faster. It uses GTK+2, avahi for MPD server detection and curl to
 download remote files (like cover arts and lyrics). Various plugins are provided
 like audioscrobbler/last.fm submission or multimedia keys support.
<<